**Overview**
This dashboard provides an overview of the alerts ingested from Github Code Scanning, Secret Scanning, and Dependabot.

The dashboard provides an overview of code scanning, secret scanning, and dependabot alerts that are open and resolved. It deep-dives into the top 10 repositories where alerts are found. The dashboard presents a view of alerts by severity. The dashboard gives a view alerts by type of GHAS Product.

[**Integrations Page**](/app/integrations/detail/github/overview)
